  <a href="#top">Back to top</a>
  <h2>Creating Kitahs</h2>
  <%= image_tag "new_kitah_index.png"%>
  <p>To create a new kitah, you must be logged in as an administrator. Begin by clicking the "Kitahs" link at the top of your screen.  At the bottom of the list, there is a link to "New kitah". Click this link </p>
  <%= image_tag "create_kitah.png"%>
  <p>You are now looking at the new kitah form. Select one or more teachers from the list provided. If you need a teacher who is not listed, check their user role and make sure it is set to 'teacher'. You can select multiple teachers by holding the 'control' (sometimes written as 'ctrl') button on your keyboard while clicking each teacher. Next type in the name of the Kitah. This name must be unique to the kitah. You also have the option of selecting the grade fields for this kitah. Again, select more than one by holding 'control' while clicking each desired field. These fields will be show up on the report cards for the students in this kitah. The selected teachers will be able to enter grades for these fields for the students in this kitah. When you are done, press the "create kitah" button. You will then see the created kitah and its information, including students. The kitah was just created so there will not be students.
  <a href="#top">Back to top</a>
