  <h2>Entering Students</h2>
  <%= image_tag "admin_students.png"%>
  <p>To enter a new student, you must be logged in as an administrator. Begin by clicking the "Students" link at the top of your screen.  At the bottom of the list, there is a link to "New Student". Click this link </p>
  <%= image_tag "student_form.png"%>
  <p>You are now looking at the new student form. Enter the students information on the fields provided. Note that the grade field represents the numeric grade they are in (ie: enter 1 for a 1st grade student, 5 for a 5th grade student). Next, select the kitah the student will be in. When you are done entering the information, press "create student".</p>
