  <h2>Creating Grade Fields</h2>
  <%= image_tag "grade_fields_index.png"%>
  <P>To create a new Grade Field, you must be logged in as an administrator. Begin by clicking "Grade Fields" at the top of your screen. This will bring up the Grade Fields Index page. Click the "create new grade field" link at the bottom of the screen. Existing Grade Fields can be edited from this page by typing in a new name for them and pressing 'update' at the bottom of the screen.</p>
  <%= image_tag "create_grade_fields.png"%>
  <p>This brings up the page shown above, where you can enter the name of the new Grade Field. After entering the name, press 'Create Grade Field'. This will create the Grade Field and return you to the previous index page, showing the new Grade Field added to the list. If you want to remove the grade field, click the "Archive" link next to it. This keeps the grade field from showing up on the list. However, if students have grades for this gradefield, those grades will remain for those students.</p>
  <a href="#top">Back to top</a>
