  <h2>Adding Grade Fields to Kitah</h2>
  <%= image_tag "edit_kitah.png"%>
  <P>To create a new Grade Field, you must be logged in as an administrator. Begin by clicking "Kitahs" at the top of your screen. This will bring up the Kitahs Index page. Click the "edit" link next to the Kitah you want to add Grade Fields to. This opens the Edit Kitah page seen above.</p>
  <%= image_tag "multiple_grade_fields_selected.png"%>
  <p>On this page, you see the list of available Grade Fields at the bottom. Only the selected Grade Fields will be attributed to this Kitah. If you want to select more than one, press and hold the "control" key on your keyboard then click each Grade Field you want to add. Then release the "control" key and click "Update Kitah". You will now see the Kitah with the updated list of Grade Fields.</p>
