  <h2>Entering Grades For A Student</h2>
  <%= image_tag "select_student_for_grades.png"%>
  <P>To enter grades for a student, you must be logged in as an administrator or a teacher. Begin by clicking "Student Grades" at the top of your screen. This will bring up the Students Grades Index page. Select the student whose grades you want to change from the drop-down menu and press 'Go'. This will take you to the students' grade page. If no grades have been entered yet, this page will be blank. Click the 'edit grades' link to continue to edit the grades.</p>
  <%= image_tag "edit_student_grades.png"%>
  <p>This page shows the Grade Fields available for the student and their current grades, if any. Enter or change the grades as needed. When done, press "update". This taks you back to the students' grade page and show the updated grades.</p>
