  <h2>Entering Grades For A Kitah</h2>
  <%= image_tag "kitah_students_for_grade_change.png"%>
  <P>To enter grades for a Kitah, you must be logged in as an administrator or a teacher. Begin by clicking "Kitahs" at the top of your screen. This will bring up the Kitahs Index page. Find the Kitah whose grades you want to change and click on "show". This will take you to the kitah's page. Select the first student whose grades you want to change and click the "Edit Grades" link as shown above. This takes you to the student's grade page. Follow the instructions above for editing the grades. After updating the grades and returning to the student's grade page, click the link to return to their kitah's index page. Repeat for the remaining students.</p>
